<HEADLINE>
<P>
BAKERY SING! FOCUSES ON OSCAR WINNERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The best Oscar-winning songs will be the focus of the next Sing! Sing! Sing! 
program Sunday at 4 p.m. at the Jazz Bakery, 3221 Hutchinson Ave. in Culver 
City. 
</P>
<P>
 Among songs scheduled on the program dating from 1934 include "You'll Never 
Know," "High Noon," "Moon River" and "The Shadow of Your Smile." 
</P>
<P>
 Sing! Sing! Sing! has presented its "mature" sing-along program monthly for 
two years. 
</P>
<P>
 Admission for the Oscar program is $10, which includes cost of a sing-along 
sheet and refreshments. 
</P>
