<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE WAY OFF BROADWAY PLAYHOUSE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Jan Herman 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The 1994 Season: 
</P>
<P>
 * Through April 10: "Red Scare on Sunset," by Charles Busch. 
</P>
<P>
 * May 28-July 31: "Light Sensitive," by Jim Geoghan. 
</P>
<P>
 * Sept. 2-Oct. 16: "Some of My Best Friends," by Stanley Hart. 
</P>
<P>
 * Nov. 26-Dec. 23: "Greetings," by Tom Dudzick. 
</P>
<P>
 All productions will be at the Way Off Broadway Playhouse, 1068 E. 1st St., 
Santa Ana. (714) 547-8997.Jan Herman 
</P>
